elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xxl{font-size:59px}<\/style><h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">O que \u00e9 Benchmarking?<\/h4>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e358c1c e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"e358c1c\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f308ef3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f308ef3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.16.0 - 20-09-2023 *\/\n.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-stacked .elementor-drop-cap{background-color:#69727d;color:#fff}.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-framed .elementor-drop-cap{color:#69727d;border:3px solid;background-color:transparent}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap{margin-top:8px}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap-letter{width:1em;height:1em}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap{float:left;text-align:center;line-height:1;font-size:50px}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap-letter{display:inline-block}<\/style>\t\t\t\t<p>O benchmarking \u00e9 muito mais do que apenas uma palavra da moda no mundo dos neg\u00f3cios. Trata-se de uma pr\u00e1tica estrat\u00e9gica que envolve a compara\u00e7\u00e3o sistem\u00e1tica de processos, produtos ou servi\u00e7os de uma <a href=\"https:\/\/www.socialhub.pro\/quem-somos-2\/\">empresa<\/a> com os l\u00edderes do setor, buscando identificar as melhores pr\u00e1ticas e oportunidades de melhoria.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e0bfefe e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"e0bfefe\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bdfd966 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"bdfd966\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Em sua ess\u00eancia, o benchmarking \u00e9 uma ferramenta de aprendizado cont\u00ednuo, permitindo que as organiza\u00e7\u00f5es identifiquem \u00e1reas para aprimoramento, adotem novas abordagens e, em \u00faltima an\u00e1lise, alcancem um desempenho superior.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-49eaa47 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"49eaa47\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b4f3b66 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b4f3b66\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Tipos de Benchmarking\n<\/h4>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-953f2d4 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"953f2d4\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b872839 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b872839\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>1. Interno:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Compara\u00e7\u00e3o de processos dentro da pr\u00f3pria empresa.<\/li><li>Identifica\u00e7\u00e3o de melhores pr\u00e1ticas entre diferentes departamentos.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-92ca494 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"92ca494\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ec72f2f elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ec72f2f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>2. Externo Competitivo:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Avalia\u00e7\u00e3o do desempenho em rela\u00e7\u00e3o aos concorrentes diretos.<\/li><li>Identifica\u00e7\u00e3o de oportunidades para superar a concorr\u00eancia.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bad867c e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"bad867c\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-46208f1 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"46208f1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>3. Externo Funcional:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Compara\u00e7\u00e3o com organiza\u00e7\u00f5es fora do setor, mas com processos semelhantes.<\/li><li>Adapta\u00e7\u00e3o de pr\u00e1ticas inovadoras de outras ind\u00fastrias.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5ce0e0d e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"5ce0e0d\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f666b6e elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f666b6e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>4. Gen\u00e9rico:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Foco em pr\u00e1ticas gerais de gest\u00e3o e operacionais.<\/li><li>Busca por inspira\u00e7\u00e3o em diversas fontes.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-88038e9 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"88038e9\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6f92871 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"6f92871\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Como fazer um Benchmarking?<\/h4>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3e6cb22 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"3e6cb22\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8dcc299 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8dcc299\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Compreendendo os objetivos:<\/strong><\/p><p>Antes de embarcar na jornada do benchmarking, \u00e9 crucial ter uma compreens\u00e3o clara dos objetivos que se deseja alcan\u00e7ar. Isso pode incluir aprimoramento de processos, redu\u00e7\u00e3o de custos, aumento da satisfa\u00e7\u00e3o do cliente ou inova\u00e7\u00e3o de produtos. Definir metas espec\u00edficas ajudar\u00e1 a orientar todo o processo.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9be3b54 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"9be3b54\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e41c648 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e41c648\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Escolhendo os parceiros certos:<\/strong><\/p><p>Selecionar as empresas ou organiza\u00e7\u00f5es que servir\u00e3o como refer\u00eancia \u00e9 uma etapa cr\u00edtica. Opte por aquelas que s\u00e3o l\u00edderes em seus setores ou que demonstram pr\u00e1ticas excepcionais nas \u00e1reas que voc\u00ea deseja melhorar. Considere tamb\u00e9m o benchmarking interno, comparando diferentes departamentos dentro da sua pr\u00f3pria organiza\u00e7\u00e3o.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ca4ea0a e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"ca4ea0a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7de4c41 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7de4c41\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Definindo m\u00e9tricas relevantes:<\/strong><\/p><p>M\u00e9tricas bem escolhidas s\u00e3o a espinha dorsal do benchmarking. Elas devem ser espec\u00edficas, mensur\u00e1veis e alinhadas aos objetivos definidos anteriormente. Essas m\u00e9tricas podem abranger desde efici\u00eancia operacional e qualidade do produto at\u00e9 satisfa\u00e7\u00e3o do cliente. A precis\u00e3o das m\u00e9tricas garantir\u00e1 uma compara\u00e7\u00e3o significativa.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8459873 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"8459873\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ba6412b elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ba6412b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Coletando dados de maneira sistem\u00e1tica:<\/strong><\/p><p>A coleta de dados \u00e9 uma fase crucial do benchmarking. Desenvolva um m\u00e9todo consistente e eficiente para reunir informa\u00e7\u00f5es relevantes. Isso pode envolver entrevistas, an\u00e1lise de documentos, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.google.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">pesquisa de mercado<\/a> e outras abordagens. Lembre-se de respeitar a confidencialidade das informa\u00e7\u00f5es sens\u00edveis durante esse processo.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5f29d80 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"5f29d80\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-68305f4 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"68305f4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Analisando e comparando resultados:<\/strong><\/p><p>Com os dados em m\u00e3os, \u00e9 hora de mergulhar na an\u00e1lise comparativa. Examine cuidadosamente os resultados, destacando semelhan\u00e7as, diferen\u00e7as e padr\u00f5es. Identifique as pr\u00e1ticas que se destacam positivamente e aquelas que podem inspirar melhorias em sua pr\u00f3pria organiza\u00e7\u00e3o.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7eb694f e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"7eb694f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-721249a elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"721249a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t